@node Future "The Future of SmartFile"

@{b}The Future of SmartFile@{ub}

This is only the first version of SmartFile. Many more features may come in
leter versions. Mail @{"me" link Author} to suggest more or say which you
thinkare most important.

How much gets done on SmartFile depends on how many people register, so if
you want to see more features in SmartFilr, support it by registering.


@{b}Proposed future features@{ub}

* Preferences Editor

* Selectable file views
    Including a tree view and a workbench style icon view!

* More dynamic gadgets (like Rename)

* Built in commands (make some operations a little faster)

* Notification for updating directories


and anything else you suggest


@endnode





